extends base.pug

block style
  style
    include ../public/css/blog.css

block content
  .blog-container
    .blog-header
      h1 About Art Fusion
      h2 Your Destination for Handcrafted Excellence
    
    .blog-content
      // Introduction
      p.intro Art Fusion is more than just a marketplace - it's a thriving community where artisans and art enthusiasts come together to celebrate creativity in all its forms.

      // Our Story Section
      section.art-section
        h2 Our Story
        p Started in 2024, Art Fusion was born from a simple idea: to create a space where artisans could showcase their unique creations and connect directly with art lovers. Today, we're proud to host thousands of handcrafted items, from intricate glass art to cozy fiber creations.

      // Our Mission Section
      section.art-section
        h2 Our Mission
        p.highlight We believe that every piece of art tells a story, and every artisan deserves a platform to share their craft with the world.
        
        h3 What We Offer:
        ul
          li 
            strong For Artisans: 
            | A supportive platform to showcase and sell your creations to a global audience.
          li 
            strong For Buyers: 
            | Access to unique, handcrafted pieces that you won't find anywhere else.
          li 
            strong For Everyone: 
            | A community that celebrates creativity, craftsmanship, and artistic expression.


